'''Jaclyn Werlein''' was a patient who was pregnant with a baby who needed a valvuloplasty.

==History==
Jaclyn was 23 weeks pregnant when an echo confirmed critical aortic stenosis in her fetus. She was taken into surgery for a valvuloplasty to treat the condition. The procedure was successful.

==Relationships==
===Romantic===
As her husband fainted the last time they talked about needles, he had been sent to the gift shop when the doctors came in to talk to Jaclyn.

===Familial===
Jaclyn was 23 weeks pregnant when she had surgery to repair a defect in her fetus's heart.
